前确有困难，可以记账，分期或延期付款。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"86fa429432","type":"paragraph","text":"5、公社应找给生产队的资金，找不找？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"97d25dd06a","type":"paragraph","text":"应该找。有现钱就现找，目前无力的公社应转账或抵59年的上交。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"aaff98403f","type":"paragraph","text":"6、对困难户的照顾资金从哪里来？","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"a678f8124a","type":"paragraph","text":"确有困难的由生产队积累中的公益金适当给予解决。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"d72dcb6bc5","type":"paragraph","text":"7、生产队的上交部分，交不出来怎么办？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"dd306395cc","type":"paragraph","text":"记账分期上交或59年补交。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"006b996f51","type":"paragraph","text":"8、生产队的公共积累留多少？公社为了发展的需要。可不可以突破上缴15%的比例？","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"15d0af5d10","type":"paragraph","text":"坚持省委提出的3～15%，社员的工资、供给和生产费以外，其余部分可作为生产队的积累，公社不应突破15%的比例。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"8b98ba4779","type":"paragraph","text":"9、储备粮属于哪里处理？大队、公社要不要储备粮？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"57fca7292a","type":"paragraph","text":"各生产队的储备粮属于生产队自己处理，但不能有私买私卖等违法行为。大队、公社也应当储备些。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"33f43f27b9","type":"paragraph","text":"10、已转入公社的生猪、山羊、水产等，目前还分散在生产队经营，如何处理？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"0775903eb9","type":"paragraph","text":"如属小型的畜牧场、大型水库等需要公社经营的仍归公社经营；不宜于公社经营的，扣除投资交生产队经营。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"67d6d868d2","type":"paragraph","text":"11、大队与大队、生产队与生产队、手工业加工的互利问题怎么解决？","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"16403a4c12","type":"paragraph","text":"应按规定付给工资。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"59ed33531f","type":"paragraph","text":"12、原搞大协作吃的粮食结算不结算？","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"a7f790335c","type":"paragraph","text":"应该结算，谁吃谁把粮。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"a81684af3a","type":"paragraph","text":"13、经济作物区供应粮的口粮钱从哪里来？","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"fe0e48d488","type":"paragraph","text":"已交公社的应由公社退回口粮钱，未交公社的应由自己负责。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"4ac4a1237a","type":"paragraph","text":"14、大协作的工分怎样处理？","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"1acf95f8cd","type":"paragraph","text":"如属防洪抢险等特大自然灾害，应教育群众，发扬共产主义风格，义务支援。如属于一般生产协作，应记工付酬。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"d764303cea","type":"paragraph","text":"15、在大办钢铁时多吃的粮食怎样解决？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"2e8c2dc406","type":"paragraph","text":"如果吃本队的粮食，应列入全年口粮标准之内，如多吃了别单位的粮食，应照数偿还。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"87ee820064","type":"paragraph","text":"16、一个公社内穷、富队工资、供给标准悬殊过大，公社怎样进行必要的调节？","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"e43a55427f","type":"paragraph","text":"穷队与富队之间工资、供给水平，公社应该承认有一定的差别，只在确定上交任务时适当调节。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"ae994c0628","type":"subtitle","text":"二、关于财务计划管理问题","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"3592e3de12","type":"paragraph","text":"17、公社内部物资的调剂如何处理？","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"485cae9216","type":"paragraph","text":"物资调剂应按国家价格，由调入单位付款。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"6eb46a5e69","type":"paragraph","text":"18、基本建设哪里投资？","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"de88fc6cb1","type":"paragraph","text":"属于公社的由公社投资。属于几个队共同利益的由几个队合办。属于一个队收益的小型基本建设应由生产队投资办理。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"f4293429a7","type":"paragraph","text":"19、农具修理添配和耕牛添配资金从哪里来？","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"94c7a004fb","type":"paragraph","text":"由生产队负责。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"ea9bf651c2","type":"paragraph","text":"20物资等价交换是否通过公社统一办理？","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"5d6691699b","type":"paragraph","text":"必须通过公社做好通盘计划，进行交换。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"df267dd958","type":"paragraph","text":"21、生产队里小型工厂、畜牧场归谁投资？","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"05593f4571","type":"paragraph","text":"由生产队投资。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"245379ca01","type":"paragraph","text":"22、参观评比时公社发给的奖励金从哪里开支？","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"897b32f6a1","type":"paragraph","text":"公社主持的由公社开支。大队主持的由大队开支。生产队支持的由生产队负责。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"5953c5056c","type":"paragraph","text":"23、前一段公社主持的副业收入归公社、大队还是生产队？","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"f92dc0b9ba","type":"paragraph","text":"应归公社的收入交公社，但公社应给予抽出劳力的生产队的一定的报酬。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"53f5e15d99","type":"paragraph","text":"24、插花田调动的投资成本怎么办？","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"daa2616ad6","type":"paragraph","text":"按投资成本计算，由拨入单位付给。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"48c29fcd7d"},{"id":"b05e47ec07","type":"paragraph","text":"25、公社、大队生产队已买了的脚踏车、收音机等怎样处理？","inde